          "reviewBody": "I paased out this year , so the school rn is working really good . Some of the staff is strict , but it is needed for the kids to get disciplined . The  teachers provide correct information to the students when he or she needs to get studying about a particular subject . The sports sector of the school is not that good and efficient as it needs to be. The ground of the school is huge enough to play several sports at a time but teachers only let students play selected sports. The school has all the things to improve the sports sector and has scope for improvement.\n\nINFRASTRUCTURE - 4.5/5\nSTAFF - 4/5\nSPORTS - 3.5/5\nRULES AND REGULATIONS - 4/5\nMAINTENANCE - 4/5",
